\par\pard\plain \tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\sa60\sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf3 Village of Romperando, in the northern part of Kahilabek. The village is located in a northeastern section of Kahilabek that was once part of the province of Tobaloon. It was ceded to the Kahila folk in the Settlement of Bryktool, at the conclusion of the period known to Heliops as The Trouble with the Kahila. This was the same Settlement that granted the woods south of Juuj, formerly claimed by the Kahila, to Juujal.}
