\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf3 - Need to define in more detail what/who are \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93the Kahila\u8221\'94, as distinct from other southerners and easterners, and separately from their association with criminal organizations.}
\par\plain \f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf3
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf3 - Need to elaborate, if only for background, on the structure of the leading/controlling Helioptic organizations and personalities. }
\par\plain \f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf3
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf3 - Generally speaking, I have a lot of protagonists and not very many antagonists. Lots of good guys, but not so many bad guys and the one I have tend to be vague, amorphous \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93others\u8221\'94. Need to use Tonedo as the foil, the tip of the spear, for the \u8220\'93bad\u8221\'94 Heliops. When they are defeated in Act Three, we need to see his downfall.}
